# Markdown Syntax Guide

## Headings

# Heading 1
## Heading 2
### Heading 3
#### Heading 4
##### Heading 5
###### Heading 6

---

## Links

[Link Text](https://www.example.com)
[Link with Title](https://www.example.com "This is a tooltip")

---

## Text Formatting

**Bold Text**  
*Italic Text*  
***Bold and Italic***  
~~Strikethrough~~

---

## Lists

### Unordered List
- Item 1
- Item 2
  - Sub-item
* Another item

### Ordered List
1. First item
2. Second item
   1. Sub-item

---

## Code

### Inline Code
Use `code` inside a sentence.

### Code Block
```python
def hello():
    print("Hello, world!")
```

---

## Images

![Alt text](https://via.placeholder.com/150 "Optional title")

---

## Blockquote

> This is a quote.  
>> Nested quote.

---

